title: Helene Fischer - Rausch Live - Die Arena Tour
overview: With 71 incredible concerts and more than 750,000 tickets sold, Helene Fischer's "Rausch - Die Arena-Tour" 2023 has thrilled people like no other artist ever before. ARD is showing the pop icon's concert highlight unabridged and with all the hits, thrilling acrobatics and elements of fire and water in a perfectly staged show.
